      "raw_text": "Probably no subject of public in\nterest in recent years has attracted\nsuch wide attention or spread so\nrapidly as that of dry farming.\nFour gatherings have been held\nfor the discussion of this subject\nand preparations are now going\nfor the fifth convention Of the\nDry Farming Congress and Inter-\nnational Dry Farming exposition,\nwhich will be held in Spokane the\nfirst week in October"
